name: Empathic
Payoff: Tuning in on the experiences of people and mechanics of technological systems.

name: Inventive
Payoff: Creating new harmonic combinations for people and technology based on existing knowledge, insights and experiences.

name: Profiling
Payoff: Presenting in an attractive way so that people identify with what they see.

name: Balanced
Payoff: Determing if something is (about to be) out of balance and preventing or restoring the balance.

name: Analytic
Payoff: Quickly processing large amounts of information to get to the core of a subject.

name: Solutions oriented
Description: Understanding relevance of knowledge, insights and experiences when finding solutions.

name: Decisive
Payoff: Quickly anticipating needs with little signals.
